sequenceDiagram
  %% Diagram 72: API Gateway Request Lifecycle and Version Governance Flow

  autonumber
  actor C as Client
  participant G as API Gateway
  participant Policy as Version Policy
  participant Sec as Auth + Throttle + Validation
  participant R as Route Resolver
  participant H as Domain Handler
  participant Shape as Response Shaper

  C->>G: Request /api/v1/... with token
  G->>R: Resolve API version and route
  R->>Policy: Check version support and deprecation window
  alt Unsupported/deprecated version
    Policy-->>G: Version not supported
    G-->>C: Version error + migration guidance
  else Version valid
    G->>Sec: Apply auth, rate limit, DTO validation
    alt Security gate fails
      Sec-->>G: Reject reason
      G-->>C: 401/403/429/400 response
    else Security gate passes
      G->>H: Execute domain operation
      H->>Shape: Apply response contract and headers
      Shape-->>G: Versioned response + trace id
      G-->>C: Versioned response
    end
  end
